{"tid":2215906,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（聽誠話，跟誠走）丹麥養老基金盡沽中国股債","createTime":"2020-09-24T09:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T10:28:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6236ca82f99fa61d4abd20dca2c832e6bf4d7f3d","tid":2215906,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:56:36.000Z","msg":"丹麥養老金公司AkademikerPension在官網公布，決定將中國排除在投資領域之外，現在將會出售總值近4億丹麥克朗（約4.87億港元）的政府債券和股票，並將資金投資到其他地方。AkademikerPension負責人Jens Munch Holst，基金一直長期觀察中國，認為系統地侵犯人權，不能再對它視而不見。<br />\n<br />\nAkademikerPension指，基金理念是平衡投資回報和社會責任，由於要承擔社會責任，因此很難將中國納入投資組合中。此前，AkademikerPension已剔除了沙特阿拉伯，泰國和伊朗等國家。<br />\n<br />\n負責人指，AkademikerPension最重要的任務是確保會員獲得良好的退休金，以在需要時繼續生活，但基金同時也承擔着社會責任，因此在這種情況下，必須對中國撤資。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2761744</code></pre>"},{"pid":"0bf1b27bfcd6977e7af4ad8cef4c8fedcdf99c8b","tid":2215906,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T09:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9dce234248f73453c30edc8d42e9245b558dafc","tid":2215906,"uid":331421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:11:43.000Z","msg":"相比起中國講沽美債講極都未沽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"accd4a086d4feee707716a7afaeb1c7975cb8511","tid":2215906,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:12:31.000Z","msg":"12/10前？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b545745637f612776e01cfe772abb4fcc939dc8","tid":2215906,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:28:58.000Z","msg":"真係走資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}